Muffin-Donald
#############

.. _description:

**Muffin-Donald** -- Its a plugin for Muffin_ framework which provides support
for asyncronous tasks

.. _badges:

.. image:: https://github.com/klen/muffin-donald/workflows/tests/badge.svg
